---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Know Jesus"
  description="Learn about Jesus Christ — who He is, why He came, and how you can begin a personal relationship with Him today."
>

  <PageHero
    eyebrow="The Most Important Decision"
    title="Know Jesus"
    subtitle="God loves you deeply and has an incredible plan for your life. Here's how to begin a relationship with Him."
    breadcrumb={[{ label: 'Know Jesus', href: '' }]}
    size="lg"
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kj-layout">

        <div class="kj-main">

          <!-- The Problem -->
          <div class="kj-block">
            <div class="kj-step">01</div>
            <h2>We All Have a Problem</h2>
            <p>The Bible says that the wages of sin is death, and that we all have sinned and fallen short of the expectations of God (Romans 3:23, Romans 6:23). This sin created a separation between us and our Creator — a gap that no amount of good works, religious effort, or self-improvement can bridge.</p>
            <p>But this is not the end of the story. In fact, it's only the beginning.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- The Solution -->
          <div class="kj-block">
            <div class="kj-step">02</div>
            <h2>Jesus is the Answer</h2>
            <p>God loved the world so much that He sent His only Son, Jesus Christ. Jesus lived perfectly — the only truly sinless person who ever walked this earth. He willingly went to the cross and took on every sin, sickness, and burden that was meant for us.</p>
            <p>"Jesus, who knew no sin, became sin, so we through Him might become the righteousness of God." (2 Corinthians 5:21)</p>
            <p>Three days after His death, Jesus rose from the dead — defeating sin and death forever. This resurrection is the foundation of our faith and the guarantee of our hope.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- The Invitation -->
          <div class="kj-block">
            <div class="kj-step">03</div>
            <h2>You Are Invited</h2>
            <p>Through Jesus, you can be fully restored to God. Not through your own effort or performance — but through simple faith in what Jesus has already done for you. God offers salvation as a free gift. All you have to do is receive it.</p>
            <p>"If you confess with your mouth that Jesus is Lord and believe in your heart that God raised him from the dead, you will be saved." (Romans 10:9)</p>
          </div>

          <!-- The Prayer -->
          <div class="prayer-box">
            <div class="prayer-label">A Simple Prayer</div>
            <p class="prayer-intro">If you would like to begin a relationship with Jesus today, you can pray something like this:</p>
            <blockquote class="prayer-text">
              "Father God, I come to You today. I acknowledge that I have sinned and that I need You. I believe that Jesus Christ is Your Son — that He died for my sins and rose from the dead. I ask You to forgive me of all my sins. I receive Your gift of salvation. Thank You for taking my place and dying for me. I welcome You to be the Lord of my life. In Jesus' name, Amen."
            </blockquote>
            <p class="prayer-note">If you just prayed this prayer, we'd love to celebrate with you and help you take your next steps in faith!</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:.5rem;">
              Let Us Know — We'd Love to Hear From You
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <aside class="kj-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card highlight-card">
            <h4>God Values You</h4>
            <p>You are not an accident. God has an incredible plan for your life — a plan that begins with knowing Him personally.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h4>Need Prayer?</h4>
            <p style="font-size:.875rem; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:1rem;">Our team would love to pray for you. Call or message our prayer line anytime.</p>
            <div class="prayer-contact">
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 01-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 01-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 013.07 11.5a19.79 19.79 0 01-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 012 .84h3a2 2 0 012 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 00.7 2.81 2 2 0 01-.45 2.11L6.09 8.91a16 16 0 006 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 012.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 002.81.7A2 2 0 0122 15.92v1z"/></svg>
              <a href="tel:+12106502087">+1 (210) 650-2087</a>
            </div>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" style="margin-top:1rem; width:100%; justify-content:center;">Send a Message</a>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h4>Next Steps</h4>
            <ul class="next-steps">
              <li>
                <div class="step-dot">1</div>
                <span>Tell someone about your decision</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="step-dot">2</div>
                <span>Start reading the Bible (begin with the Gospel of John)</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="step-dot">3</div>
                <span>Find a community — join us this Sunday</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="step-dot">4</div>
                <span>Get water baptized as a public declaration</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-navy btn-sm" style="margin-top:1.25rem; width:100%; justify-content:center;">Connect With Us</a>
          </div>
        </aside>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Banner -->
  <section class="section-sm" style="background:var(--navy); text-align:center;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:600px;">
      <h2 style="color:#fff; font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:.75rem;">Ready to Take the Next Step?</h2>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.65); font-size:1rem; line-height:1.75; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Whether you just made a decision for Christ or you have questions — we are here for you. Come as you are.</p>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
        <a href="/about"   class="btn btn-outline-white">Learn About Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .kj-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px; gap: 3.5rem; align-items: start; }

  /* Main content */
  .kj-block { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; padding-bottom: 2.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .kj-block:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .kj-step { font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .14em; color: var(--gold); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
  .kj-block h2 { font-size: 1.65rem; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .kj-block p  { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: .9rem; }

  /* Prayer box */
  .prayer-box {
    background: var(--navy); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 2.5rem; margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .prayer-label {
    font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .14em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold-light); margin-bottom: .75rem;
  }
  .prayer-intro { font-size: .95rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.65); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .prayer-text {
    font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.88); line-height: 1.85;
    font-style: italic; border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .prayer-note { font-size: .88rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: .75rem; }

  /* Sidebar */
  .sidebar-card {
    background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .sidebar-card h4 {
    font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .12em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: .9rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }
  .highlight-card { background: var(--gold); border-color: var(--gold); }
  .highlight-card h4 { color: rgba(255,255,255,.75); }
  .highlight-card p { font-size: .9rem; color: #fff; line-height: 1.7; }
  .prayer-contact {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .6rem;
    font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy);
  }
  .prayer-contact a { color: var(--navy); }

  /* Next steps */
  .next-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .75rem; }
  .next-steps li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: .75rem; font-size: .875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }
  .step-dot {
    width: 22px; height: 22px; background: var(--navy); color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: .68rem; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .kj-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .kj-sidebar { order: -1; }
  }
</style>
